Most companies establish their sale and purchase processes so that the entered documents must be reviewed by responsible persons and approved for further processing. The topics of this part explain how you can configure the approval maps for sales orders, purchase orders, purchase requests, and purchase requisitions. ==In This Part==[anchor|#table_hjd_ydl_ldb] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#ul_ijd_ydl_ldb] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__con_Approvals|Sales Order Approval] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\PO__con_Purchase_Order_Approvals|Purchase Order Approval]
| [anchor|#ul_jjd_ydl_ldb] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__How_Set_Up_Approval|To Set Up Approval of Sales Orders] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__How_Create_Map_SO_Approval|To Create a Map for Sales Order Approval] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__How_Approve_Order|To Approve a Sales Order] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\PO__how_Set_Up_Approval|To Set Up Approval of Purchase Orders]
