The topics of this chapter describes how to process a return of inventory items. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_e18eff61-c021-4af0-8830-1ead13e8aa96] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#ul_jyv_bv2_1x] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__con_scn_Return_for_Credit_wShip|Return for Credit with Receipt] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__con_scn_Return_for_Credit|Return for Credit Without Receipt] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__con_scn_Return_for_Cash|Return for Cash] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__con_scn_Return_Replacement|Return for Exact Replacement] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\SO__con_scn_AuthReturn|Merchandise Authorization Return]
