row.Content:
Purchase orders in Acumatica ERP can include multiple lines of different line types; the type a particular line has depends on the settings of the item specified in the line. The line type indicates how the system processes this purchase order line. {br}
The topics of this part describes the line types, the settings you can configure to affect the purchase workflow for these types of lines, and the line completion rules for each line type. ==In This Part==[anchor|#_e18eff61-c021-4af0-8830-1ead13e8aa96] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#ul_jyv_bv2_1x] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\PO__con_Purchase_of_Stock|Stock Item Lines in Purchase Orders] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\PO__con_Purchase_of_NStock_w_Receipt|Non-Stock Lines in Purchase Orders] *[HelpRoot_OrderMgmt\PO__con_Purchase_of_Services|Service Lines in Purchase Orders]
